data.title: Homecoming Weekend
data.text:
If you arrived early for Homecoming Weekend, join us for a concert and come out to cheer on the Big Red!

(#) Indicates Building Number on the Campus Map

Fine Arts Performance—Wednesday, October 9

Fall Ensemble Concert—7:00 p.m.

The concert will feature performances by the Concert Band, Concert Choir, and Unaccompanied Minors (our contemporary a cappella group).

Location: Kimberly Chapel (33)

Girls Varsity Tennis Match (Portage High School—Portage, WI)

Varsity vs. Aquinas, Logan, Black River Falls, West Salem, Lodi, Edgerton, Lake Mills WI, Luther, Watertown Luther Prep, Portage, Columbus, Altoona, Mauston, Edgewood, Viroqua—9:00 a.m.

Big Red Athletics—Thursday, October 10

Girls Volleyball in Lindsay Gym (5)

JV vs. University Lake School—6:00 p.m.

Varsity vs. University Lake School—7:30 p.m.
